quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  18,60,"Moshe o ile a re ho mosebeletsi oa hae: “Ruri nke ke ka emisa ho fihlela ke fihlile mateanong a maoatle a mabeli, le ha ke qhala lilemo-lemo tseleng"
  18,61,"Empa eitse ha ba se bafihlile mateanyetsong, ba lebala Tlhapi ea bona, eona e ile ea inkela tsela ea eona ka har’a metsi e le bolokolohing"
  18,62,"Hoba ba tsamae sebakanyana, eaba o re ho mosebeletsi oa hae: “A k’u re etsetse lijo tsa hoseng. Ruri! Haele leetong lena re teane le mathata a mangata.”"
  18,63,"A araba a re: “Na ha o oa bona, hore nakong eo re neng re ts’abela holim’a lefika, ke ile ka lebala tlhapi teng, – ke satane ea entseng hore ke lebale ho buoa ka eona, – e ile ea inkela tsela ea eona ka har’a metsi ka mokhoa o makhethe.”"
  18,64,"Moshe a re: “Sena ke sona seo re neng re tsomana le sona.” Kahoo, menahana le mehlala ea bona"
  18,65,"Ke moo ba ileng ba fumana e mong oa makhabunyane a Rona, eo Re mo sitsitseng ka Mohau oa Rona le ho mo ruta tsebo e tsoang boteng ba Rona"
  18,66,"Moshe a re ho eena: “Na nka o sala morao ho fihlela moo o tlang ho nthuta ‘Nete eo o ileng oa e rutoa?”"
  18,67,"Eaba eo o re: “Ruri u ke ke oa ba le mamello ho ‘na"
  18,68,Ho tla joang hore u ka ba le mamello ka seo u sa kang oa ba le kutlisiso e feletseng ka sona?”
  18,69,"Moshe a re: “Haeba e le thato ea Allah, Ruri u tla mphumana ke ena le mamello, ha ho letho leo ke tlang ho u hanyetsa ka lona.”"
  18,70,"Eo a re: “Ho lokile, haeba u tsamaea le ‘na; u se mpotse letho ho fihlela e le ‘na ea ka o bolellang sona.”"